verbose_text: Indeed, although Deltatrx1Deltatxl1 cells contain similar total levels of Pap1 protein to other strains (XREF_FIG B, whole-cell lysates), when extracts were prepared under nondenaturing conditions (which do not preserve the in vivo thiol-redox state), Pap1 levels were markedly lower in Deltatrx1Deltatxl1 cells than in other strains (XREF_FIG B, soluble proteins).
